# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Track links — shown in the INFO dialog when access=granted or access=check.
# Upload this file to:
#   Cloudflare → afest-assets/twysted/radio/track-links.dat
#   (optional GitHub fallback: webiste_TD/radio/cfded/track-links.dat)
#
# FORMAT per track block (========== delimiter between blocks):
#
#   id              = must match the audio filename stub (e.g. td-audio001) —
#                     derived by stripping "-normal.mp3", "-high.wav", "-off.mp3"
#                     from the first File: entry in signal.dat.
#
#   grantedMessage  = 0                    → use default message from index.html
#                     (any other value)    → override; HTML allowed
#                                            (e.g. <b>BOLD</b>, &nbsp; etc.)
#                     Used when access=granted. Followed by link= lines that
#                     belong to the granted bucket.
#
#   checkMessage    = same rules. Followed by link= lines for the check bucket.
#                     Optional — omit if the track has no "check" state content.
#
#   ---             = separator line (3+ hyphens) divides the two buckets.
#                     Parser also auto-switches on checkMessage=/grantedMessage=,
#                     but the visible separator makes files easier to scan.
#
#   link            = Service Name | URL   → one line per streaming service
#                     Service Name | 0     → placeholder (skipped — service N/A)
#                     Belongs to whichever bucket is currently active.
#
#   message         = legacy alias for grantedMessage (still supported; do not mix
#                     with grantedMessage= in the same block).
#
# ACCESS STATES (set in signal.dat; affect dialog behavior here):
#   access=granted  → green, uses grantedMessage + granted-bucket links
#   access=check    → orange, uses checkMessage + check-bucket links
#   access=none (or anything else) → red, "nag us" IG prompt (no links shown)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

